# init(first:second:)

**Initializer**

Initializes an object representing the outputs of the web authentication PRF extension.

## Declaration

```swift
init(first: SymmetricKey, second: SymmetricKey?)
```

## Discussion

Call this method only if the registration request includes input values. Otherwise, use [doc://com.apple.authenticationservices/documentation/AuthenticationServices/ASAuthorizationPublicKeyCredentialPRFRegistrationOutput-swift.struct/supported] or [doc://com.apple.authenticationservices/documentation/AuthenticationServices/ASAuthorizationPublicKeyCredentialPRFRegistrationOutput-swift.struct/unsupported].
